Meteara would have smiled, if she did not feel anything else than 
hatred.

Meteara: And approaching so near of me was foolish of you!

She activated her electrical weaponry and tendrils of electricity rose 
around her, and would effectilely damage her opponent.

Meteara: Now, either you go and tell everyone on the Vector that the 
Vok are not pleased, or you shall stay silent forever!
